<br />\n轉灣驚唔驚睇錯邊，入左相反方向？<br />\n<br />\n我唔想變fast and furious<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"美國揸車最重點分別係，紅燈但係無行人過馬路嗰陣可以右轉。如果係十字路口想左轉，通常都會有左轉燈。係左轉燈熄左，而你嗰條線重係綠燈，你可以&ldquo;吞&rdquo;前半個車位，等到對面方向無車黎，而左轉嗰邊都無行人，你就可以左轉（通常要等到黃燈都先可以有機會轉）。若果有寫明no turn on red，就記得左轉燈一熄就唔可以轉。<br />\n<br />\n我第一次揸左軚一d都唔驚，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">因為我係LA考車牌</span>。反而我係香港揸，試過幾次行錯reverse 方向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"美國揸車冇咩行人呢個因素，所以好易揸。左右唔係問題，記得司機位永遠都係響條路（計晒兩邊對行方向）嘅中間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住見到Stop sign，要停。十字路口四面都係stop嘅話，係先停低（即係早過你黎呢個路口）嘅車先行。其實係等於排隊，不過亞洲歐洲都冇呢個方法，有時d人以為係對家讓你去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLA去Vegas會悶到抽筋，中途d路又直又長，記得帶red bull同power bar。以前我返bay area會順路買橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e9bdce9234fa954e7878a0acf89accd48099c5","tid":1892960,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"台灣揸過，at車好快上手"},{"pid":"f999f940a80bc86561e3ef1640cbfe823bf5c69f","tid":1892960,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"揸左軚始終無右軚咁好睇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己個邊都唔敢攞咁貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80be0ff7eef26b4727a5ac494d7b095d21a3a32","tid":1892960,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db3e5e996b0e25c7b0ecfecb3ff4cfdda8b21296","tid":1892960,"uid":147871,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHoFVVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu